{"label": 1, "text": "Therefore a right knowledge of breathing is a part of the science of life."}
{"label": 1, "text": "But the deeper meaning is, that the spiritual man, when he has gained poise through right effort and aspiration, can stand firm, and guide the currents of his life, both the incoming current of events, and the outgoing current of his acts."}
