{"label": 1, "text": "When the two processes are equally balanced, the true onepointedness is attained."}
{"label": 1, "text": "Everything has these two sides, the side of difference and the side of unity; there is the individual and there is the genus; the pole of matter and diversity, and the pole of oneness and spirit."}
{"label": 1, "text": "To see the object truly, we must see both."}
