{"label": 1, "text": "So we may once more use the same illustration."}
{"label": 1, "text": "Perfectly concentrated Meditation, perfect insight into the chrysalis, reveals the caterpillar that it has been, the butterfly that it is destined to be."}
{"label": 1, "text": "He who knows the seed, knows the seed-pod or ear it has come from, and the plant that is to come from it."}
