{"label": 1, "text": "In the eternal Now, both past and future are consummated."}
{"label": 1, "text": "Bjorklund, the Swedish philosopher, has well stated the same truth: Neither past nor future can exist to God; He lives undividedly, without limitations, and needs not, as man, to plot out his existence in a series of moments."}
